Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.94,0:00:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些臭蟲們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.99,0:00:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌引來他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:00:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.81,0:01:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.23,0:01:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可以將功贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞開身心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展露你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又舊地重遊…

Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:26.22,ENG,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fad(600,450)\pos(940,577)\shad0\bord2\be1}Last Frontier

Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來 這裡就是一切的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告稱2040年初次遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8年後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是11年前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支第117次調查船團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功捕獲神秘生物Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並開始研究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究者中也包括那位格蕾絲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟用真名正大光明地混入Frontier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 早發現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第117調查船團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團長是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪奧·諾姆博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始文明研究第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是蘭歌在「鳥之人」中扮演的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲馬 看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論文的草稿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於空間水晶與植入技術實現超時空網絡的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蕾絲·奧格娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了醫療記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭雪·美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蘭歌的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭雪·美博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最初的V型感染症患者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,患病的母體懷胎並生下了蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是蘭歌她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量的來源
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是根據論文推測的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河規模的完全即時植入網絡概念圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把空間水晶作為植入體的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理論上在銀河兩端都不會產生延遲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.59,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為現實的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為銀河規模的超並列思維網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不想被人知道自己的思維
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再偷偷想 「好男人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河統一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這理想聽來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 也有貓膩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非完全的並列思維
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為結點的端子上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對其他終端有優越性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把它們集約化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終的中央一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會相對於其他成為上位存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配銀河嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為是說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有個很大的障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再方便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.91,0:06:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能讓全部人類都植入化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此才需要Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗者只有死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受者成為下屬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕易跨越斷層
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連反應彈也奈何不了的Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類沒有對抗手段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而其中的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是唯一能與Vajra進行交流的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra網絡的粒子協議解析
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,92.3%完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:06:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真單純
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:07:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算監聽Vajra之間的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,始終難以解析的協議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦轉換成人的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能如此輕易被解析
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪奧博士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的血會互相傷害 開始自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會證明我是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類會超越原始文明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把判明的事實傳送給了新統合政府
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 通信延遲和議會表決…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對趕不上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有靠我們做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會跟我來吧 莫妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶回來的文件裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有寄給瑪奧博士的信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士有個孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「決定把媽媽的耳環送給女兒」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算邁入宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的生活還是沒有變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相愛而結合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生兒育女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後歌與文化被代代傳頌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐天下父母心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼理所當然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超時空網絡是多此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們必須去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 凱茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離敵防空圈4萬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知全艦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信代號設定為「Sierra Bravo」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在那些怪物身上吃夠了苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.14,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而Frontier船團正面臨絕境
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們終於找到了蟲子的母星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須不惜一切代價全滅它們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求得生存
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在敵人母星在數萬隻Vajra組成的防禦網保護下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次作戰的最大目標是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破Vajra防禦網
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊敗中樞部女王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時讓主島降落行星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那顆行星成為我們新的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀河妖精謝麗爾·諾姆的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會引導我們走向勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝各位好運
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去 馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.45,0:10:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也許不會高興吧 米歇爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我終究是天頂星人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去心愛的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法默不做聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.91,0:10:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊部隊的維度吞噬者搭載情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在完成97%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我卑鄙也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你 七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算豁出性命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非戰鬥人員移動前往主島
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居住衛星降落行星的作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入所有能量與物資
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂背水一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗原本就意味著滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那顆行星是我們最後的開拓地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願宇宙的真理向我們微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間波的浪濤會穿越因果律與時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的歌聲如果會毀滅我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會殺死蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰應該已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這場戰鬥中活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想來告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 無法獨自飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了這道理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.71,0:12:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遲鈍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無言以對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人遊戲到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 謝麗爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在聽到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定都無法繼續唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都別說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部結束後 聽你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救出蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到的話 就聽你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回來 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:13:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住吧 這麼好的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打著燈籠也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將抵達作戰宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始前TIME-60
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也沒有掛念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等燃盡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有音樂和我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入敵人制空圈內
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子的動靜如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈陣速度是通常的1/3以下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發現有組織行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效啊 這歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有搞頭 有搞頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報仇雪恨的日子到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這星球是我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會進入混戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆跟緊我屁股飛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被擊中 涅涅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是臨陣磨槍的機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見吧 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想侵犯這顆星球的人正大舉攻來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護這顆美麗的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親也一定希望這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正被分割孤立
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁熱打鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令主島降落地上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織性在恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音 難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間波受到干擾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra軍戰鬥力增強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 蘭歌·李
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果真背叛了人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在繼續唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是她真正的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra的網絡對蘭歌的歌起到增幅作用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra的攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這首歌更合適的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的鑰匙在我手中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的寶座已歸我所有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要置我們於死地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離我妹妹遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓蘭歌做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們兄妹的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從侵略者手中保護Vajra生活的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵略者？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你們先來襲擊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先侵犯領土的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消逝吧 到銀河的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座1號中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是生命的閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯多的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝麗爾的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭歌的歌聲 馳騁天際
